y covers an area of large will affect the benefits.For the overall revenue, we need to reduce the floor space as much as possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. The pan-geographic UPS power room monitoring system is composed of three parts: front-end device, client/server APP and PC large-screen terminal.Users can check the operation status and relevant parameters of the UPS device in real time after logging in through the client APP/PC, and can also visualize the operation status and relevant data of the care system on the large screen of the mobile phone.When an exception occurs, the alarm message can be received synchronously.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;4. When the load peaks, if the power supply of the grid is insufficient, lithium battery can coordinate the power supply and reduce the input of mains power, thus reducing the cost.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://7j1y9l.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/image/k2o2jlzc_6bkidhdornk05dc37bd5cb21f.png&quot; title=&quot;2.png&quot; alt=&quot;lithium battery&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','21','0','0','About lithium battery UPS, you may not know!-Industry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','lithium battery use life cycle is longer than the battery.Because of the lower replacement frequency, the cost of lithium battery is more economical than the battery, so the use of lithium battery will be more widespread.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1573092415','1573699546','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('24','Industry dynamic','What are the reasons for the bulging deformation of UPS power battery?','/tmp/uploads/20191107/29179fcd21269a012cb1ce9c4d73f3e5.png','&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;UPS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;power battery application for a long time, sometimes there will be a drum bag deformation phenomenon, in fact, no matter what type of battery, including our commonly used mobile phone battery, use for a long time will also appear drum phenomenon.The bump is very bad for battery use and can even cause an explosion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;The bulge and deformation of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.xdlxny.cn/battery/Industrial-lithium-battery.html&quot;&gt;UPS power battery&lt;/a&gt; are mainly caused by the increase of internal pressure stimulation brush. The main reasons are as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;(1) in the charging operation of sealed battery, especially in the series UPS power battery, if the battery has been charged, if there is a bad quality of the battery will often appear bad internal gas compound phenomenon, so as to bulge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;(2) the opening pressure of the relief valve is too high, or the relief valve is blocked.When the pressure in the body increases to a certain extent, the valve cannot open normally, in this case is bound to cause swelling deformation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;(3) as the sealed battery is of lean liquid design, there is a way to avoid the combination of gas. If there is &amp;quot;rich liquid&amp;quot; phenomenon, the generated O2 will be prevented from diffusing to the negative electrode, reducing the compound rate of O2 and increasing the pressure in the body.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Malgun Gothic&amp;quot;, Meiryo, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;(4) floating charge pressure is set too high, charging current is large, leading to the rapid precipitation of O2 on the positive plate, and too late in the negative compound, at the same time, UPS power battery temperature rise is also fast, in the exhaust, the pressure reached a certain level, make the battery bulge deformation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','26','1','0','What are the reasons for the bulging deformation of UPS power battery?-Customized lithium battery-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','USP power battery application for a long time, sometimes there will be a drum bag deformation phenomenon, i','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1573098415','1573699525','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('30','Industry dynamic','Points for attention in changing lead-acid battery into lithium battery','/tmp/uploads/20191118/a4b80476131c5ef012c7cee1288dd884.jpg','&lt;p&gt;When changing lead-acid battery into lithium battery, we need to pay attention to the following points&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1, space&amp;nbsp;of the battery &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is feasible to&amp;nbsp;change&amp;nbsp;lead-acid battery into lithium battery,If the batteries have the same capacity&amp;nbsp;and voltage,&amp;nbsp;but it is necessary to consider whether the size of the battery can still be installed in the original position, whether it is protruding or being squeezed, because squeezing and being affected by damp will cause damage to the battery and short-circuit phenomenon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2,Battery chargers must be used to meet battery specifications&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Even if the lead-acid battery and the lithium battery capacity voltage is the same, also can not share chargers, because the two&amp;nbsp;kinds of&amp;nbsp;battery&amp;nbsp;need different charging voltage and current at different stages.When lead-acid batteries are charged, the charger voltage is high.However, lithium battery has higher technical requirements, so when charging, the charger adopts constant current and constant charging, charging lithium-ion batteries&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;with lead-acid battery chargers can lead to overcharging, and there is a risk of explosion&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3, replacement&amp;nbsp;of socket&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Because the interfaces of lead-acid battery and lithium battery are&amp;nbsp;different, for the battery must be matched with the socket.You can&amp;#39;t just plug it in, it is easy to lead to the lithium battery short circuit, thus dangerous.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4, You&amp;nbsp;can not use the original charging port for charging&amp;nbsp;after changing the battery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Because of the different charging principle, if the original charging port of the electric vehicle is used for charging, the circuit will be damaged and the lithium battery will be short-circuited.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5, The controller does not need to replace&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It should be mentioned again that the battery can only be replaced with the same capacity and the same voltage, but not with the previous battery capacity and voltage, which will burn out the controller and damage electrical components such as the motor hall.As long as it is consistent with the galvanic cell capacity voltage, there is no need to replace the controller.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','0','1','0','Points for attention in changing lead-acid battery into lithium battery-Industry dynamic -Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','It is feasible to change lead-acid battery into lithium battery,If the batteries have the same capacity and voltage, but it is necessary to consider whether the size of the battery can still be installed in the original position','','1574046296','1574046443','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('25','Industry dynamic','Advantages and disadvantages of ternary lithium battery','/tmp/uploads/20191108/d40a440982ce2afc0483a3842c97deae.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Ternary lithium battery is balanced in capacity and safety.It is a kind of battery.The main functions, advantages and disadvantages of the three metal elements are as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Co3+ : reduce cationic mixed occupancy, stabilize the lamellar structure of the material, reduce impedance value, improve conductivity, improve circulation and multiplier performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Ni2+ : it can improve the capacity of the material (increase the volume energy density of the material). However, due to the similar radius of Li and Ni, too much Ni will misplace with Li, resulting in li-ni misplacement. The higher the concentration of nickel ion in the lithium layer, the more difficult it is to remove lithium from the layered structure, leading to poor electrochemical performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Mn4+ : it can not only reduce the cost of materials, but also improve the safety and stability of materials.However, too high Mn content will easily occur spinel phase and destroy the layered structure, reducing the capacity and cyclic attenuation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;High energy density is the biggest advantage of ternary lithium batteries, the platform is an important indicator of the battery energy density and voltage, determines the basic performance and cost of batteries, the higher the voltage platform, the greater the specific capacity, so the same volume, weight, and even the same ampere hour battery, high voltage platform ternary material lithium battery life is longer.The discharge voltage platform of single ternary lithium battery is as high as 3.7v, the lithium iron phosphate is 3.2v, and the lithium titanate is only 2.3v. Therefore, from the perspective of energy density, the ternary lithium battery has an absolute advantage over lithium iron phosphate, lithium manganese acid or lithium titanate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;Poor safety and short cycle life are the main disadvantages of ternary lithium battery, especially safety performance, which has been a major factor limiting its large-scale allocation and large-scale integration.A large number of measured results show that the large-capacity ternary battery is difficult to pass safety tests such as acupuncture and overcharge, which is also the reason why the large-capacity battery generally introduces more manganese elements or even USES lithium manganate mixed together.With a cycle life of 500 cycles, the battery is in the lower middle of the range. Therefore, the main application area of ternary lithium battery is consumer electronics products such as 3C digital products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','19','1','0','Advantages and disadvantages of ternary lithium battery-Industry-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Ternary lithium battery is balanced in capacity and safety. It is a battery with excellent comprehensive performance.','','1573203045','1573699513','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('26','Industry dynamic','Lithium ion battery performance of five decisive factors','/tmp/uploads/20191111/715bb8f4f8e4eecdc6615717a66e6d15.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The performance of lithium ion battery is mainly related to the electrochemical performance of lithium ion battery.The electrochemical performance parameters of lithium ion battery mainly include the following five aspects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Rated voltage: the rated voltage of commercial lithium ion &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.xdlxny.cn&quot;&gt;battery&lt;/a&gt; is generally 3.6v (at present, some 4.2v lithium ion battery products have appeared in the market, but the proportion is not large), the operating voltage range is 4.1~ 2.4v, and there are also lower limit termination voltage set as other values, such as 3.1v.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Rated capacity: the capacity obtained at 0.2c constant discharge to termination voltage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;1C capacity: refers to the capacity obtained at the 1C constant discharge voltage to the termination voltage.The 1C capacity is generally smaller than the rated capacity. The smaller the difference, the better the battery&amp;#39;s current characteristics and the stronger the load capacity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;High and low temperature performance: lithium ion battery high temperature up to +55℃, low temperature up to -20℃.In this ambient temperature range, the battery capacity can reach more than 70% of the rated capacity.Especially in the high temperature environment generally has little impact on the battery performance.Charge-holding capacity: the percentage of the rated capacity to the capacity obtained by discharging at 0.2c after the battery is left open for 28 days after full charge.The larger the value, the stronger the charge-holding ability and the smaller the self-discharge.The charge-holding capacity of a typical lithium-ion battery is more than 85%.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(247, 248, 250); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Cycle life: with the lithium ion battery charging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;discharg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;, battery capacity reduced to 70% of the rated capacity, the number of charg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and discharg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;obtained is called cycle life.Lithium ion battery cycle life is generally more than 500 times.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','13','1','0','Lithium ion battery performance of five decisive factors-lndustry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The performance of lithium ion battery is mainly related to the electrochemical performance of lithium ion battery.The electrochemical performance parameters of lithium ion battery mainly include the following five aspects.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1573453834','1573698546','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('27','Industry dynamic','What are the main factors that generate heat inside lithium batteries?','/tmp/uploads/20191111/7cada4fb500b79e1f008da143e926c23.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The temperature variation of a lithium battery system is determined by the generation and emission of heat, which can be caused by thermal decomposition and/or reaction between battery materials.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;When a part of the battery deviates, such as internal short circuit, large current charging&amp;nbsp;,discharging&amp;nbsp;and overcharging, a large amount of heat will be generated, resulting in an increase in the temperature of the battery system.When the battery system reaches a certain temperature, it will lead to a series of reactions such as decomposition, so that the battery is thermal damage.And because the liquid electrolyte in a lithium battery is an organic compound that makes it flammable, the battery can catch fire when the temperature of the system is high.When the heat generated is not high, the temperature of the battery system is not high, and the battery is in a safe state.The reasons for heat generation in lithium batteries are mainly described below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(1) the reaction between the battery electrolyte and the negative electrode. Although there is a layer of interfacial protective film between the electrolyte and lithium metal or carbon material, the reaction between them is limited by the existence of protective film.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(2) thermal decomposition exists in the electrolyte. When the lithium battery system reaches a certain temperature, the electrolyte will decompose and generate heat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(3) reaction between electrolyte and positive electrode. Since the decomposition voltage of lithium battery electrolyte is higher than the voltage of positive electrode, the reaction between electrolyte and positive electrode rarely happens.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(4) thermal decomposition of cathode materials;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(5) thermal decomposition of anode materials;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(6) enthalpy change of positive and negative active substances;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(7) the current generates heat through the internal resistance;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(8) in addition, for lithium battery, the negative electrode potential is close to the electrode potential of lithium metal, so in addition to the above reactions, the reactions with adhesives, etc. should also be considered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','18','1','0','What are the main factors that generate heat inside lithium batteries?-lndustry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The temperature variation of a lithium battery system is determined by the generation and emission of heat, which can be caused by thermal decomposition and/or reaction between battery materials.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1573454011','1573699494','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('31','Industry dynamic','What is the highest temperature the lithium battery can withstand?','/tmp/uploads/20191118/20cb33fa17991153c2669b3b9efac1a7.jpg','&lt;p&gt;Lithium ion battery has been widely studied and appliedas a new generation of energy storage technology, but almost&amp;nbsp;can&amp;nbsp;only work in room temperature environment.High or low temperature&amp;nbsp;will reduce&amp;nbsp;the performance&amp;nbsp;of lithium battery .Especially in high temperature conditions, the internal heat will produce a larger floating, resulting in explosion and other safety accidents.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The temperature limit of mobile phone lithium battery is generally 40-60 degrees, and the explosion-proof valve is usually marked on the battery, while the high-temperature lithium battery can withstand the highest temperature of 800 degrees.General lithium battery in withstand high temperature test, there are 200 degrees, 500 degrees and 800 degrees, but usually, it&amp;nbsp;will not be exposed to such a high temperature&amp;nbsp;in daily life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For lithium battery, there is no clear theoretical support for the internal resistance, discharge platform, life, capacity and other necessary relations under various temperature performance in the industry, and relevant calculation formulas and mathematical models are still in the exploratory stage.In general, lithium-ion batteries are not sensitive to temperatures between 0 and 40 &deg; c, but beyond that, life and capacity are compromised.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In order to ensure the life and safety and reliability of lithium battery, advanced protection management system will be adopted in the battery pack of high-temperature lithium battery to prevent overcharging, overdischarging, high-temperature operation, low-temperature charging, or short circuit from being damaged, or even safety problems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','17','1','0','What is the highest temperature the lithium battery can withstand?-Industry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium ion battery has been widely studied and appliedas a new generation of energy storage technology, but almost can only work in room temperature environment.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1574046410','1574046410','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('33','Industry dynamic','We get the danger of lithium-ion battery from these respects','/tmp/uploads/20191120/e26349ed721a11425eaca5629ddcd074.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium ion battery is a potentially dangerous chemical power source because of its chemical characteristics and system composition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1 high chemical activity&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium is the I - group element in the second period of the periodic table.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2 high energy density&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The specific energy of lithium ion battery is very high (&ge;140Wh/kg), which is several times of that of nickel cadmium, nickel hydride and other secondary batteries. In case of thermal runaway reaction, high heat will be released, which will easily lead to unsafe behavior.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3 organic electrolyte system is adopted&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The organic solvent of organic electrolyte system is hydrocarbon, the decomposition voltage is low, easy to oxidize, and the solvent flammable;In case of leakage, the battery will catch fire or even burn or explode.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4 has a high probability of side reactions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium ion battery in the normal use of the process, its internal electrical energy and chemical energy conversion between the chemical forward reaction.However, under certain conditions, such as overcharging, overdischarging or overcurrent operation, it is easy to cause chemical side reactions inside the battery.If this side reaction intensifies, it will seriously affect the performance and service life of the battery, and may produce a large amount of gas, which will make the pressure inside the battery increase rapidly and then explode and catch fire, leading to safety problems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;5 The structure of electrode material is unstable&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The overcharging reaction of lithium ion battery will change the structure of the anode material and make the material have a strong oxidation effect.Moreover, this effect is irreversible, and the heat generated by the reaction, if accumulated, will be in danger of causing runaway heat.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','0','0','0','We get the danger of lithium-ion battery from these respects-Industry dynamic -Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium ion battery is a potentially dangerous chemical power source because of its chemical characteristics and system composition.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1574228895','1574228895','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('34','Industry dynamic','The advantage of lithium battery for solar street light','/tmp/uploads/20191120/38d72d8ca79e8fceceb691b9db7b2eca.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The efficient energy-saving advantages&amp;nbsp;of solar street light&amp;nbsp;make it widely promotion and application ,there are&amp;nbsp;three kinds&amp;nbsp;of battery as the&amp;nbsp;important components of solar street light , respectively is the lithium iron phosphate batteries, lead-acid battery and gel battery, among them, the lithium iron phosphate batteries&amp;nbsp;get the favour of the solar industry &amp;nbsp;more and more&amp;nbsp;because of its higher &amp;nbsp;service life&amp;nbsp;than other kinds&amp;nbsp;.So ,what are the advantages of lithium batteries?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Lithium battery belongs to dry battery nature:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;A controllable, pollution-free energy storage battery is more stable and safer than lead-acid batteries.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. Intelligent optimization calculation and reasonable distribution of power grade:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium battery&amp;nbsp;for solar street light can also be based on the user&amp;#39;s demand for the remaining capacity of the battery, day and night time, weather conditions and other factors for intelligent optimization calculation, reasonable distribution of electricity levels, and achieve the light control, time control and storage memory and other functions, to ensure that the rainy day continues to light.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Long life of lithium battery:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Different from the short life of lead-acid battery, which needs to be replaced within two or three years, the service life of lithium battery is generally more than 10 years. In the solar street light system, the service life of LED light source is generally up to 10 years (about 50,000 hours). The choice of lithium battery can perfectly match the system and avoid the tedious process of frequent battery replacement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','11','1','0','The advantage of lithium battery for solar street light-Industry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The efficient energy-saving advantages of solar street light make it widely promotion and application ,there are three kinds of battery as the important components of solar street light','','1574232125','1574232125','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('35','Industry dynamic','Why solar street lamps use lithium batteries?','/tmp/uploads/20190924/53d43e9f8f457d192f228b6cb8a784ab.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;With the deepening of the construction of new socialist countryside and beautiful countryside, solar street lamps as the first choice of lighting equipment can be seen everywhere.Solar street lamps are&amp;nbsp;not only energy saving and environmental protection will not generate electricity, so they are&amp;nbsp;welcomed by the people, Many solar street lamps used lithium batteries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Why are lithium batteries so popular?What are the advantages of lithium batteries over lead-acid batteries?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Lithium battery is small in size, light in weight and easy to transport.Compared with the lithium-electric energy storage system and lead-acid colloid batteries used in power solar street lamps, it weighs about a third and has a volume of about a third.In this way, the transportation is easier, and the transportation cost will naturally come down.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. Lithium battery has high energy density and longer service life.Energy density is the amount of energy stored in a given unit of space or mass.The higher the energy density of a battery, the more energy it can store per unit weight or volume.There are many factors that affect the service life of lithium battery, and energy density is a very important internal factor.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Solar street lamps with lithium batteries are easy to install.When traditional solar street lamps are installed, a battery pit is reserved, and the battery is put into a buried box to seal it.However, the installation of lithium-ion solar street lamps is much more convenient. Lithium batteries can be directly installed on the bracket, using suspended or hidden type.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4.Solar street lamp with lithium battery is easy to maintain.It only needs to remove the battery from the lamp pole or panel, while the traditional solar street lamp needs to dig out the buried battery during maintenance, which is much more troublesome than the lithium-electric solar street lamp.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','16','1','0','Why solar street lamps use lithium batteries?-Industry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','With the deepening of the construction of new socialist countryside and beautiful countryside, solar street lamps as the first choice of lighting equipment can be seen everywhere.','','1574391559','1574391665','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('36','Common problems',' Are soft-pack lithium batteries really safe?','/tmp/uploads/20191122/06da077bd8c6e0865bb573ca33c4b270.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Soft-pack lithium-ion batteries are simply liquid lithium-ion batteries with a polymer shell.In the structure of the use of aluminum plastic film packaging, in the case of security risks in the case of soft-pack batteries will only burst air.Soft-pack lithium battery has the advantages of good safety performance, light weight, large capacity, small internal resistance, flexible design and so on.There is little difference between the internal composition of soft-pack lithium battery and square and cylindrical lithium battery. The largest difference is that the soft-pack lithium battery adopts aluminum-plastic composite film as the shell, and the square and cylindrical battery adopts metal material as the shell.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Soft package of lithium battery mainly refers to the lithium battery pack shell material, if you have any packing outside, it is difficult to see, must see the battery ontology, the weight of the steel battery shell will focus than the same volume of battery, but aluminum shell and flexible packaging is not easy to distinguish, but soft, flexible packaging cells than aluminum shell with the hand break easily deformation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Are soft-pack lithium battery packs safe?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Generally speaking, soft-pack lithium battery treasure or very safe, as long as it is not violent impact, puncture, into the fire, basically very safe.Normal use, strictly follow the instructions is safe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The safety of soft-pack lithium battery is still to be improved.In fact, the root cause of combustion or even explosion of lithium battery package lies in the thermal runaway inside the battery. In essence, &amp;quot;thermal runaway&amp;quot; is a positive energy feedback cycle process: the rising temperature will cause the system to become hot, and the system will become hot and increase the temperature, which in turn will make the system become hotter. Thermal runaway is a very common phenomenon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','0','1','0',' Are soft-pack lithium batteries really safe?-Common problems-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Soft-pack lithium-ion batteries are simply liquid lithium-ion batteries with a polymer shell.In the structure of the use of aluminum plastic film packaging, in the case of security risks in the case of soft-pack batteries will only burst air.','','1574391950','1574391969','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('37','Company news','Maintenance method of Lithium battery in winter','/tmp/uploads/20191125/e0c20f417b3a428c44b4d728376e9876.jpg','&lt;p&gt;Maintenance method&amp;nbsp;of Lithium battery&amp;nbsp;in winter,Lithium batteries are easy to enter the&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;market with their&amp;nbsp;advantages&amp;nbsp;for small, light,and environmental protection, heavy, short life, heavy pollution of lead-acid batteries can not meet our needs.Lithium batteries are ready for maintenance and can last 5-7 years.Good maintenance habits can help extend the life of lithium batteries.What are the matters needing attention for maintenance of lithium battery?How does lithium battery maintain in winter?The&amp;nbsp;lithium battery manufacturers will&amp;nbsp;solve the problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maintenance of lithium battery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Generally, room temperature has little influence on the state of lithium battery, but it cannot be directly exposed to the sun. High temperature is easy to cause the model lithium battery to bulge or explode. Therefore, the model lithium battery is generally stored in an iron box or plastic box that avoids light and holds air.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Do not immerse the battery in water or make it wet;Do not stack the battery more than 7 layers;Do not transport batteries when ambient temperature is above 65℃.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2, partial discharging&amp;nbsp;of lithium battery, rather than full discharging, and to avoid frequent full discharging.Once the battery is off the production line, the clock starts ticking.Lithium batteries last only two to three years, whether you use them or not.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. The best charging environment for lithium battery is 20~26℃, which avoids outdoor high temperature charging at noon in summer and outdoor charging at night in winter.High temperature is easy to overcharge, low temperature is easy to undervoltage, the performance of lithium battery will cause a bad impact.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4, lithium battery has no memory effect, shallow charging&amp;nbsp;shallow releasing, with charging.If the battery is completely out of power before charging, it will shorten the service life of lithium battery.Even if you can last 2-3 days on a single charging, it is recommended that you charge every day.Keeping the battery in a shallow cycle state is beneficial to the extension of battery life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5. When lithium battery&amp;nbsp;is not in use for a long time, take out the lithium battery and place it in a cool and dry place.Do not freeze to avoid water vapor erosion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','11','1','0','Maintenance method of Lithium battery in winter-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Maintenance method of Lithium battery in winter,Lithium batteries are easy to enter the   market with their advantages for small, light,and environmental protection, heavy, short life, heavy pollution of lead-acid batteries can not meet our needs.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1574668460','1574755744','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('38','Company news','What is the mechanism of LiFePO4 battery charging protection?','/tmp/uploads/20191125/5b0b4b012aec5c41fdc731b5af5a6c29.jpg','&lt;p&gt;Control strategy of protection plate system for&amp;nbsp;LiFePO4&amp;nbsp;battery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Working mode&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The protection plate system of LiFePO4&amp;nbsp;battery works in static mode, charging mode and discharging mode according to the battery state.The lithium battery protection plate system is externally powered and the system start/stop is controlled by external terminals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. Protective measures&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The protection plate system of LiFePO4 battery has the following protection measures: single voltage overcharging, total voltage overcharging, overcurrent, high temperature, low temperature, short circuit, etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When the single voltage or the total voltage is overcharged, turn off the charging MOSFET and stop charging when the set protection threshold is exceeded.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Overcurrent&amp;nbsp;for charging . When the protection threshold is exceeded in 90s, the charging MOSFET is turned off and the charging is stopped.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Overcurrent&amp;nbsp;for discharging. When the protection threshold is exceeded in 90s, turn off the discharging MOSFET and stop&amp;nbsp;discharging.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Short circuit&amp;nbsp;of battery , when there is instantaneous large current immediately turn off charging&amp;nbsp;and discharging&amp;nbsp;MOSFET, the battery stop working.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Protection plate is to protect &amp;nbsp;LiFePO4&amp;nbsp;battery, so that it does not appear overcharging, overdischarging, short circuit and other problems, LiFePO4&amp;nbsp;battery protection plate&amp;nbsp;is &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;very useful, protection plate circuit can respectively detect the voltage and current of each cell&amp;nbsp;in series battery pack, control the&amp;nbsp;charging and discharging process&amp;nbsp;of battery pack .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','11','1','0','What is the mechanism of LiFePO4 battery charging protection?-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The protection plate system of LiFePO4 battery works in static mode, charging mode and discharging mode according to the battery state.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1574668536','1574755739','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('39','Company news','What are the maintenance tips for lithium ion batteries?','/tmp/uploads/20191126/299ebb87143b08d92fa3e03ed5011b61.png','&lt;p&gt;How to properly use and maintain lithium ion batteries？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lithium ion battery has the characteristics of light weight, large capacity and long life.It is the best choice of mobile phone battery, master the correct use method, can give full play to its advantages and service life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tip 1. The first three charges should be made after the battery is completely used up&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In order to reduce the self-discharge phenomenon in the process of transportation and storage, the newly delivered lithium ion battery is only charged with about 50% capacity and can be used after disassembly.&amp;nbsp;Such as the first time after the complete use and then full of use;The second time, the battery should be fully charged after being completely used, so that the battery can easily reach the best condition after three consecutive cycles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tip 2: be sure to use a lithium battery charger&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lithium ion battery must choose to charge the lithium ion battery special charger (because of its charging current is larger), otherwise it will not reach the charging effect, so that the capacity is reduced.The special charger for lithium ion battery can provide slow charge and fast charge for lithium ion battery.Lithium-ion batteries can also damage batteries if you use a non-dedicated charger.Also, don&amp;#39;t put the charger with something like a TV when you&amp;#39;re charging your battery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tip 3. Pay attention to the preservation of lithium battery after charging&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After charging, avoid placing on the charger for more than 12 hours.General lithium battery has a certain natural discharging&amp;nbsp;rate, such as completely not used, every day will still be about 1% of the electricity released.Battery performance decreases at extreme temperatures.Do not store the battery in a temperature higher than 60℃ or lower than -20℃.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','13','1','0','What are the maintenance tips for lithium ion batteries?-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium ion battery has the characteristics of light weight, large capacity and long life.It is the best choice of mobile phone battery, master the correct use method, can give full play to its advantages and service life.','','1574755726','1574755731','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('40','Company news','four key materials of power lithium battery ','/tmp/uploads/20191126/7fa3381c128e8f12a7217cae763cd5e8.png','&lt;p&gt;There are four key materials&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;power battery: negative electrode material, positive electrode material, electrolyte and diaphragm.Yue min believes that the future lithium ion battery materials must be decided by Chinese enterprises, because Chinese lithium ion battery material suppliers have realized the leap from &amp;quot;imitation - follow-up - catch up&amp;quot;, and are now on the way of &amp;quot;catching up&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the aspect of positive electrode materials, both technology and scale of domestic enterprises are forming the trend of &amp;quot;coming from behind to overtake&amp;quot;, and the future development prospect can be expected.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the aspect of cathode materials, domestic enterprises have a comprehensive leading advantage, the industry position has been formed, it is difficult to be surpassed in the short term;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In terms of electrolyte, due to the patents and core additives are controlled by foreign companies, and the formula is subject to the client, domestic electrolyte manufacturers have actually become the OEM;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the aspect of diaphragm, the domestic enterprises make slow technological progress, the new system has not achieved a breakthrough, failing to solve the problem in essence, and the industry needs to be a spoiler.Yue min said, for example, in order to improve the thermal stability of the diaphragm and the infiltration of electrolyte, domestic enterprises will generally put a layer of ceramic or organic coating on the diaphragm, up to 5 layers even, although the performance of the coating will be improved, but also take up battery space, increase the battery weight.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In addition, although battery auxiliary materials are very important, they have not been valued by domestic enterprises. Therefore, auxiliary materials have been monopolized by foreign companies for a long time and are most likely to get stuck.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','12','1','0','four key materials of power lithium battery -Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','There are four key materials of power battery: negative electrode material, positive electrode material, electrolyte and diaphragm.','','1574755837','1574755837','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('41','Company news',' the types of batteries used in lithium-ion batteries','/tmp/uploads/20191127/ec50e85e321e5c5b8ddf8fdf90502373.png','&lt;p&gt;At present, there are three types of mobile power cell in the market: 18650 cell, polymer cell, lithium iron phosphate cell.It is better for consumers to choose the best polymer lithium battery, followed by 18650 battery. Compared with the former two, the technology of lithium iron phosphate battery is not mature, and the fatal defect of large size and high price leads to the inability to scale in mobile power supply.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This paper introduces the first two types of cells.type 18650 lithium battery refers to a battery with a diameter of 18mm and a length of 65mm. 0 represents a cylindrical battery.The technology of 18650 cell is relatively mature. The battery has stable structure, high specific capacity, outstanding comprehensive performance, and can be used in many areas due to its small size.The disadvantage is that its safety is worse than the polymer lithium battery, the battery cycle is low, only about 300 times.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The difference between polymer cells and traditional lithium-ion batteries lies in the production process.Lithium batteries are coiled and soft.The polymer is superimposed and is hard in shape.Polymer and lithium batteries of the same size, the polymer capacity is larger, about 30 percent higher.It&amp;#39;s also safer and less explosive.Long service life.The times of charging and discharging reached more than 500 times.The disadvantage is the high cost, the same capacity of polymer cell than 18650 lithium ion cell at least 100% more expensive.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','0','1','0',' the types of batteries used in lithium-ion batteries-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','At present, there are three types of mobile power cell in the market: 18650 cell, polymer cell, lithium iron phosphate cell.It is better for consumers to choose the best polymer lithium battery,','','1574844764','1574844764','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('42','Company news','5 features of electric bicycle power lithium battery ','/tmp/uploads/20191127/1e66a329adf907347721dadbca284c39.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1、Long cycle life&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The charging and discharging cycle life of lithium ion battery with 1C ratio is greater than or equal to 800 times, and the electric capacity at the 800th time is greater than 70%.However, even if the lead-acid battery is discharged at 0.5C and charged at 0.15C, its cycle life is less than or equal to 350 times and its electric capacity is less than or equal to 60%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2、Light weight, small size and long endurance&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Compared with lead-acid batteries of the same size on the market, lithium-ion batteries are two-thirds the size of lead-acid batteries and about one-third the weight of lead-acid batteries.Lithium-ion batteries of the same size have more capacity than lead-acid ones, and weight loss adds about 10% to the battery&amp;#39;s range.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3、Large operating temperature range&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;It is generally found that ordinary lead-acid batteries have poor temperature adaptability, especially in winter, and their range of life is greatly affected. However, lithium ion batteries can work normally between minus 25 &deg; c and 40 &deg; c without affecting their life and range.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4、No memory effect, strong charging retention ability&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;A fully charged lithium-ion battery pack has a capacity of 95% or more after two months, while a lead-acid battery has a capacity of only 40-50% of its nominal capacity after two months.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;5、The state advocates green environmental protection products&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Compared with lead-acid batteries, which have a large amount of heavy metal lead that is harmful to the human body and the environment, lithium-ion batteries are highly environmentally friendly products that do not contain lead, mercury, cadmium and other heavy metals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','13','1','0','5 features of electric bicycle power lithium battery -Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The charging and discharging cycle life of lithium ion battery with 1C ratio is greater than or equal to 800 times, and the electric capacity at the 800th time is greater than 70%.','','1574844864','1574844864','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('43','Industry dynamic','What is lithium battery protection plate','/tmp/uploads/20191128/6dcf5fd0a07760157b57f451dadb2dc1.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium battery protection plate is the charging&amp;nbsp;and discharging&amp;nbsp;protection of series lithium battery;When fully charged, it can ensure that the voltage difference between each single battery is less than the set value (generally &plusmn;20mV), so as to realize the uniform charging of each single battery, effectively improving the charging effect under the series charging mode.Meanwhile, the state of over voltage, under voltage, over current, short circuit and over temperature of each single battery is detected to protect and extend the battery life.Under&amp;nbsp;voltage protection prevents the battery from being damaged due to overdischarging.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The lithium battery is composed of two parts: the lithium battery cell and the protective plate. The lithium battery cell is mainly composed of positive plate, diaphragm, negative plate and electrolyte.Positive plate, diaphragm, negative plate coil or cascade, packing and infusion liquid electrolyte, after packaging made from batteries, Many&amp;nbsp;people don&amp;#39;t know the effect of lithium battery protection board, lithium battery protection board ,just as its name implies is to protect lithium batteries, lithium battery protection board&amp;#39;s role is to protect the battery from overdischarging,overcharging,overcurrent and the output short circuit protection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','26','1','0','What is lithium battery protection plate-Industry-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium battery protection plate is the charging and discharging protection of series lithium battery','','1574932932','1574932932','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('44','Industry dynamic',' The operating temperature range of lithium battery','/tmp/uploads/20191128/2938c5478152b3be0b1d9790d76a1195.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Conventional operating temperature&amp;nbsp;of lithium battery&amp;nbsp;is -20℃~60℃, generally the lithium battery performance will decline&amp;nbsp;lower than 0℃,&amp;nbsp;discharging&amp;nbsp;capacity will be reduced accordingly, so the operating temperature&amp;nbsp;of lithium battery performance is commonly 0~40℃.Lithium batteries vary in temperature depending on the environment, with some operating at hundreds of degrees Celsius.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Generally speaking, the polymer battery whose working temperature can be lower than -20℃ is called low temperature polymer battery. Low temperature polymer battery is divided into ordinary low temperature polymer battery with the lowest working temperature of -40℃ and ultra-low temperature polymer battery with the lowest working temperature of -55℃.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Generally speaking, the better the low-temperature capability of low-temperature polymer battery, the worse its high-temperature performance will be. These two requirements are contradictory. At present, many lithium battery companies have developed a kind of low-temperature battery with wide temperature, which can work from -40 ℃ to -70 ℃, mainly used for products with special requirements such as on-board electronic equipment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Charging requirements, lithium battery requirements in 0℃ above, otherwise the battery will damage faster&amp;nbsp;if often be charged, , there are safety issues, discharge generally in -20~60℃.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Batteries are sensitive to temperature during use. At present, the operating temperature of lithium batteries ranges from -20℃ to 60℃.Take lithium iron phosphate, which has the highest penetration rate in China, for example, it becomes difficult to charge at sub-zero temperature, and after charging, its capacity retention rate is about 60 ~ 70% at 0℃, 40 ~ 55% at -10℃, and 20 ~ 40% at -20℃.However, when the ambient temperature of the battery exceeds 60&deg;, the lithium battery has the risk of overheating, burning and explosion as the battery works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','25','1','0',' The operating temperature range of lithium battery-Industry dynamic-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Conventional operating temperature of lithium battery is -20℃~60℃, generally the lithium battery performance will decline lower than 0℃, discharging capacity will be reduced accordingly, so the operating temperature of lithium battery performance is commonly 0~40℃.','','1574933020','1574933020','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('45','Company news','The factors that affect the price of the 18650 lithium battery','/tmp/uploads/20191211/0063fe83c0582fa5b21c3d0cf90d8bc9.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;The capacity&amp;nbsp;of 18650 lithium battery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;We know that capacity is a hotspot that most lithium battery&amp;nbsp;users are most concerned about, and usually the higher the capacity&amp;nbsp;, the more expensive it is.We know that the most stable battery capacity range of the whole 18650 lithium battery pack market is about 2200-3000mah, and the highest one can be measured at around 3200mah.Therefore, in your daily choice of cylindrical lithium batteries must choose a suitable power supply needs of the program, not blindly chasing to high capacity lithium batteries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;Internal resistance of lithium battery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;We know that there are not many home devices currently testing battery capacity and internal resistance, and for the vast majority of ordinary homes there is not much time to focus on the real parameters of lithium batteries.However, for the procurement personnel engaged in lithium battery procurement, the understanding of the internal resistance range is helpful to obtain the final price of lithium battery more accurately.Usually, the larger the internal resistance, the smaller the capacity.In those environments where power is required, the resistance value is relatively small and the price is naturally relatively high.So another factor that affects the price of a battery is its resistance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Battery shell&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;I believe that most of the time, the battery shell is not sensitive to most battery purchasers, but we have to say that the quality of the shell directly affects the final quality of the battery stability.So whether the shell&amp;nbsp;is excellent also affects its price.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','18','1','0','The factors that affect the price of the 18650 lithium battery-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','We know that capacity is a hotspot that most lithium battery users are most concerned about, and usually the higher the capacity','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1576033628','1576033628','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('46','Company news','The factors that affect the price of lithium batteries','/tmp/uploads/20191211/fb83f5ad7507d537e390cc2ca331ed2c.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The factors that affect the price of lithium batteries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The price of lithium battery has been high&amp;nbsp;since its advent , because of its cathode material, the price of different lithium battery are different.The factors that affect the price of lithium batteries are not only the differences in raw materials that lead to the great fluctuation of cathode materials, but also the following four factors that make the cost and price of lithium batteries start to fall, at the same time, their performance is also greatly improved.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The first key factor is chemical material: lithium iron phosphate batteries are made up of anode and cathode materials and electrolytes, so the underlying cost and price cannot be separated from the chemicals found in nature.Lithium batteries made from different chemical materials also cost different amounts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The second key factor is the capacity&amp;nbsp;of battery : according to statistical analysis, the larger the battery capacity, the lower the cost&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The third key factor is the scale of production: if the scale of production increases, the market will also expand, which will solve the current shortage of supply in the market, and the price of lithium batteries will naturally fall.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The fourth key factor is charging speed: charging speed is closely related to the complexity of lithium battery design, and to reduce the cost of lithium batteries, the design must be changed to accommodate faster charging.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','24','1','0','The factors that affect the price of lithium batteries-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The price of lithium battery has been high since its advent , because of its cathode material, the price of different lithium battery are different.','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1576033742','1576033742','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('47','Company news','What are the real reasons for the lithium battery bulging?','/tmp/uploads/20191224/122b0c44a356c3fc194a3d2040df5c0d.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;There are two main reasons for the swelling of lithium battery. One is the problem made by the manufacturer. The manufacturing environment is bad, the manufacturing equipment is old, and so on.All these may make the lithium battery pack in the use of the phenomenon of bulging, even more dangerous.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Another reason lies in the user itself. If the user uses&amp;nbsp;lithium battery products improperly, such as overcharging or discharging, or continuous use in extremely harsh environment, lithium battery may also cause a bulge.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;In addition to the above two main reasons, there is a less common reason.That is, the battery is not used for a long time, and then it is not well preserved.When it is exposed to the air for a long time and not used, and full of electricity.Since the air is conductive to some extent, leaving it too long is equivalent to direct contact between the positive and negative electrodes of the battery, which causes a chronic short circuit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The main principle behind the bulging of lithium batteries is that the inside of the battery produces a violent reaction that is similar to a short circuit, generating a large amount of heat, which leads to the decomposition and gasification of electrolytes, and the lithium battery will bulge.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;When a lithium battery pack has a bulging problem, it&amp;#39;s best not to continue using the battery with the problem.Because of the expansion of the cell, when the expansion to a certain limit may cause an explosion, which is very dangerous.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','18','1','0','What are the real reasons for the lithium battery bulging?-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','There are two main reasons for the swelling of lithium battery. One is the problem made by the manufacturer. ','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1577178656','1577178656','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('48','Company news','Why is lithium battery suitable for UPS power battery?','/tmp/uploads/20191224/624542414bba09526ce68964356a22c2.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Lithium battery UPS have a longer service life than lead-acid batteries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium iron phosphate battery, charged and discharged at room temperature 1C, the monomer after 2000 cycles, the capacity is still more than 80%, 3C cycle life reaches more than 800 times.Lead-acid batteries, on the other hand, last about 300 cycles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. Compared with lead-acid batteries, lithium batteries are less polluting and environmentally friendly&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium iron phosphate battery pack is greener than ordinary lead-acid battery, free of any heavy metals and rare metals, non-toxic, little environmental pollution, can avoid the common battery replacement of environmental pollution.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Advantages of anode and cathode materials and raw materials of lithium batteries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4. Market advantages of UPS lithium batteries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The use of lithium battery in UPS power supply battery has begun to take shape in China (accounting for more than 65% of the international market), the history of lead-acid battery out of the stage for the development of environmental lithium power create an unparalleled opportunity, electric vehicle battery generation has emerged in various places, lithium battery UPS power supply is expected to break out in the next two years, and become a big player in the battery industry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','17','1','0','Why is lithium battery suitable for UPS power battery?-Company news-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium iron phosphate battery, charged and discharged at room temperature 1C, the monomer after 2000 cycles','Industrial lithium battery,Customized lithium battery','1577178726','1577178726','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('49','Company news','Safety requirements for polymer lithium batteries','/tmp/uploads/20200106/d58e69f01524581d60ad4ce7f7132ed1.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;We all know that lithium polymer batteries in actual use, it is forbidden to overcharge, discharge, exceed standard battery for charge and discharge, because the charge and discharge will affect the safety and service life of batteries, use more than the standard large current charge or discharge batteries in can cause thermal fusion phenomenon, serious can cause leakage or fire, endanger the life property safety, so in polymer lithium battery in the actual work needs to be a safe protective measures, to avoid the risk of polymer lithium battery caused by misuse.Polymer lithium battery protection plate should have the following basic functions:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Overdischarge protection: when the lithium polymer battery is about to run out of power, the voltage reaches a required minimum value, the protection plate will be closed and cannot discharge again, so the product will automatically shut down, forming an overdischarge protection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. Overcharge protection: when charging polymer lithium battery products and the voltage reaches the highest voltage (4.2v), the protection plate will automatically power off and close, indicating that the battery will not continue to be charged at full charge.The formation of an overshoot protection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Short circuit protection: when the polymer lithium battery is accidentally short circuit, the protection plate will automatically close within a few milliseconds and will not be energized. At this point, the positive and negative poles will also be free to meet a piece, forming a short circuit protection will not cause the explosion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4. Overcurrent protection: when the lithium polymer battery is discharged, the protection plate will have a maximum current limit. Different products are different.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;5. As well as the safety and anti-failure function design and anti-static shock design of the polymer lithium battery protection plate itself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','5','1','0','Safety requirements for polymer lithium batteries-Lithium battery price in China-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Overdischarge protection: when the lithium polymer battery is about to run out of power, the voltage reaches a required minimum value, the protection plate will be closed and cannot discharge again,','','1578275120','1578275120','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('50','Industry dynamic','The reason for the inconsistency of lithium battery pack','/tmp/uploads/20200106/f1e523062e2db779a67d925d5b3009a9.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Firstly, there are technological problems and uneven materials in the manufacturing process, which lead to slight differences in lithium battery materials;After the lithium battery is put into use, the electrolyte density, temperature, ventilation conditions, self-discharge degree and charging and discharging process of each battery in the battery may be affected by differences, and the capacity and internal resistance of the battery of the same batch out of the factory may be different.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. During loading and using, electrolyte density, temperature, ventilation condition, self-discharge degree and charging and discharging process of each battery in lithium battery pack are affected by differences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;What are the hazards and problems caused by inconsistent lithium battery packs?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The capacity loss, cell monomer form lithium battery pack, capacity in line with the &amp;quot;wooden barrel principle&amp;quot;, the worst that the capacity of the cell determines the capacity of the entire battery pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(2) life loss, small capacity cell, every time is full, put out too much, very likely to be the first to reach the focus of life.The end of the life of a cell, a group of welded together, also followed the end of life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(3) the increase of internal resistance, different internal resistance, flow through the same current, internal resistance of the cell heat relatively more.The battery temperature is too high, resulting in accelerated deterioration, and the internal resistance will be further increased.Internal resistance and temperature rise, forming a pair of negative feedback, so that high internal resistance cell accelerated deterioration.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','4','0','0','Why do lithium batteries need protective panels-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','During loading and using, electrolyte density, temperature, ventilation condition, self-discharge degree and charging and discharging process of each battery in lithium battery pack are affected by differences.','','1578275703','1578275703','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('51','Company news','Do you know the main advantages of soft-pack lithium batteries?','/tmp/uploads/20200107/c6e149cf4b220c922df252381ef3e4b3.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(1) good safety performance: the electrolyte of the soft-clad battery is less leaky, and the soft-clad battery will burst under the circumstance of potential safety hazards, instead of exploding when the battery is overpressed like the hard-shell battery;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(2) light weight: the weight of the soft-clad battery is 40% lighter than that of the square steel battery with the same capacity, and 20% lighter than that of the square aluminum battery;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(3) large battery capacity: the soft package can save 20% of the volume, 50% higher than the steel shell battery of the same size, and 20-30% higher than the aluminum shell battery;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(4) good cycling performance: the soft-clad battery has a longer cycle life, and the 100-cycle attenuation is 4% ~ 7% less than that of the aluminum shell;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(5) the small internal resistance, soft package of battery internal resistance is small lithium-ion batteries, domestic minimum do below 35 m &Omega;, greatly reduce the since the power consumption of the battery;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(6) flexible design: the shape can be customized according to customer requirements, which can be made thinner, ordinary aluminum shell can only achieve 4mm, soft bag can achieve 0.5mm.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;In terms of performance, soft-pack batteries have more comprehensive advantages and broad application prospects in the future:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(1) soft-pack batteries are more suitable for portable applications that require high space or thickness, such as 3C consumer electronics;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;(2) although the single capacity of the square battery is high, it is heavy and large, while the soft-pack battery has an obvious advantage in energy density. At present, the single cell is also developing towards the direction of large capacity and high multiplier, which will better meet the requirements of mobile power supply in new energy vehicles and other fields.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','0','1','0','Do you know the main advantages of soft-pack lithium batteries?-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','good safety performance: the electrolyte of the soft-clad battery is less leaky, and the soft-clad battery will burst under the circumstance of potential safety hazards,','Chinese electric bicycle lithium battery manufacturers,Lithium battery prices for electric bicycles in China','1578384483','1578384483','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('52','Company news','What is the difference between soft lithium battery and hard lithium battery','/tmp/uploads/20200107/ea94787e19595caf223e8cd363841d77.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The weight of the&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Soft-encased lithium batteries are 40 percent lighter and 20 percent lighter than their steel - and aluminum-encased counterparts.In terms of weight, the soft-packed lithium battery is much lighter than the hard-packed lithium battery, but the main weight ratio lies in the weight of the case.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Low capacity&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Soft-clad lithium batteries are 10 to 15 percent and 5 to 10 percent higher than their steel and aluminum counterparts.Although the capacity of soft-clad lithium battery is not much higher than that of hard-clad lithium battery, there is still a certain gap between the two. For areas with high capacity requirements, the application of soft-clad lithium battery is still higher than that of hard-clad lithium battery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Low shape&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Because the internal battery of soft lithium battery is liquid, its shape can generally have a variety of shapes, which has a great advantage over the hard lithium battery in the field where there are specific requirements for the shape of lithium battery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Is lithium battery inverted soft pack or hardware good?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Lithium battery soft pack and hard pack can only be said to have their own advantages and disadvantages, soft pack lithium polymer, high safety, steel package such as 18650, most lithium ion batteries, long life.Soft bag is the original state, exhaust is better;Hard bags are better for cooling. Hard bags are safer.In fact, as long as the lithium battery pack through regular channels to buy brand products, brand products are through testing and certification, quality and safety is more guaranteed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Conclusion: compared with hard-packed lithium batteries, soft-packed lithium batteries have more or less advantages in weight, capacity, shape and other aspects. However, the existing core models of soft-packaged lithium batteries are relatively few, and the cost of developing new models is also high. Therefore, soft-packaged lithium batteries can still meet less market demand.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','4','1','0','What is the difference between soft lithium battery and hard lithium battery-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Soft-encased lithium batteries are 40 percent lighter and 20 percent lighter than their steel - and aluminum-encased counterparts.In terms of weight','Chinese electric bicycle lithium battery manufacturers,Lithium battery prices for electric bicycles in China','1578384583','1578384583','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('53','Industry dynamic','Lithium batteries have seven main advantages','/tmp/uploads/20200110/7eecadd7d4db45406840340db970ccea.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;1. Lithium ion batteries have the advantages of large capacity and high operating voltage.The battery has twice the capacity of an equivalent nickel-cadmium battery, making it more suitable for long-term communication.Conventional lithium-ion batteries have a voltage of 3.7v, three times that of nickel-cadmium and nickel-metal hydride batteries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;2. Strong charge holding capacity, allowing for a wide operating temperature range.After 30 days of open storage at (20&plusmn;5)℃, the discharge capacity of the battery at room temperature is greater than 85% of the rated capacity.Lithium ion battery has good high temperature and low temperature discharge performance, can be in - 20 ˉ + 60 ℃, high temperature and discharge performance is higher than other types of cells.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;3. Long cycle life.Lithium-ion batteries use carbon anodes.During charge and discharge, the carbon anode does not produce dendrite lithium, thus avoiding the damage of internal dendrite lithium short circuit to the battery.After 1200 consecutive charges and discharges, the battery capacity is still not less than 60% of the rated value, far higher than other types of batteries, with long-term use economy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;4. High safety, safe and fast charging and discharging.Compared with metal lithium batteries, lithium ion battery short circuit resistance, resistance overcharge, discharge, shock, vibration, shooting, acupuncture, no fire, no explosion, and so on, because it has special carbon anode electrode instead of metallic lithium electrode, thus allowing quick charge and discharge, can be in 1 c rechargeable battery charging and discharging, greatly improve the safety performance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;5. No environmental pollution.Batteries are free of harmful substances such as cadmium, lead and mercury, making them a clean &amp;quot;green&amp;quot; source of chemical energy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;6. No memory effect.It can be reused at any time, especially in wartime and emergency situations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;7. Small size, light weight and high energy.In general, lithium-ion batteries have more than twice the specific energy of nickel-cadmium batteries.Compared with similar capacity nickel-metal hydride batteries, the volume can be reduced by 30%, weight can be reduced by 50%, which is conducive to small and light portable electronic devices&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Low cost, high performance, high power, high safety and environmental protection are the development direction of lithium ion batteries.As mentioned above, lithium ion battery, as a typical representative of a new type of energy, has obvious advantages, but at the same time, there are some shortcomings that need to be improved.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','3','1','0','Lithium batteries have seven main advantages-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','Lithium ion batteries have the advantages of large capacity and high operating voltage.','Chinese electric bicycle lithium battery manufacturers,Lithium battery prices for electric bicycles in China','1578636380','1578636380','','0','1');
INSERT INTO `tp_newsa` (`id`,`titles`,`name`,`img`,`editorValue`,`num`,`home`,`sort`,`title`,`description`,`keywords`,`create_time`,`update_time`,`delete_time`,`isdelete`,`status`) VALUES ('54','Industry dynamic','What is the application scope of lithium battery UPS power supply?','/tmp/uploads/20200110/d47b774a8928507741e792c3fb865b0a.png','&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Application scope of lithium battery UPS power supply:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Banking system&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;The UPS power supply used by the bank is generally very high, and the selected UPS should have very reliable quality and high average trouble-free time. At the same time, there should be a remote operation monitoring interface, which can be monitored remotely by operators on duty or UPS maintenance personnel.Lithium battery UPS power supply is a new solution.The banking system is the largest user of lithium battery UPS, accounting for almost 40% of the whole UPS power supply sales. In the future, it will be a development trend for the banking system to adopt lithium battery UPS energy storage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Medical equipment&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;In medical equipment, available lithium battery UPS type organic UPS.Because the hospital USES a variety of medical equipment more, and the power is generally larger, resulting in the hospital&amp;#39;s power frequency fluctuations are larger, the power environment is bad.In addition, hospitals are lifesaving places, so medical equipment must be available at all times so as not to delay the emergency treatment of patients. After all, UPS equipment is valuable while life is priceless.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;Data center&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;At present, it is particularly important for the data center industry to maximize the use of existing space and minimize operating costs, especially for UPS power cooling energy consumption, battery maintenance and battery replacement service costs.Lithium battery UPS is the key to solve these problems because of its excellent performance.Lithium batteries are also lighter, reducing the total weight of a modular data center, making it easier and cheaper to transport to the installation site.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','2','1','0','What is the application scope of lithium battery UPS power supply?-Hebei Xin Dong Li New Energy Science And Technology Co.Ltd','The UPS power supply used by the bank is generally very high, and the selected UPS should have very reliable quality and high average trouble-free time. ','Chinese electric bicycle lithium battery manufacturers,Lithium battery prices for electric bicycles in China','1578638147','1578638147','','0','1');

